          API Hub menampilkan tautan dan info publik penyedia API.
          Tidak berafiliasi; merek/tautan untuk referensi, bukan dukungan.
          Gunakan sesuai kebijakan masing-masing penyedia; risiko pada pengguna.
          Beberapa penyedia API mungkin menampilkan konten vulgar, kekerasan, atau menyinggung. Harap gunakan dengan bijak; pengguna di bawah 18 tahun disarankan di bawah pengawasan orang tua/wali. Kami tidak mendukung konten tersebut dan tidak bertanggung jawab atas materi di luar kendali kami.
          Untuk koreksi/penghapusan, hubungi via form Request/Support.

title: Privacy Policy - Atlantic Server
content:
Cari server handal dengan uptime 99.9%? Atlantic Server menyediakan solusi hosting, cloud, dan VPS terbaik dengan dukungan pelanggan 24/7. Aktivasi instan! Privacy Policy
                Last updated: July 13, 2025
            

            
            
                
                    
                        1. Information We Collect
                        
                            We collect information necessary to provide and improve our services. This includes information you provide directly to us and information collected automatically when you use Atlantic Server services.
                        
                        Personal Information
                        
                            Full name and contact details (email address, phone number)
                            Billing and payment information (handled securely by payment processors)
                            Account details (username, password)
                            Any communications or feedback you provide to us
                        
                        Technical Information
                        
                            IP address and device identifiers
                            Server logs and usage data
                            Browser type and operating system
                            Performance and diagnostic data
                        
                    

                    
                        2. How We Use Your Information
                        
                            We use your information to:
                        
                        
                            Provide, operate, and maintain our services
                            Process orders and manage billing
                            Improve user experience and develop new features
                            Communicate with you regarding updates, security alerts, and support
                            Protect against fraud and ensure service security
                            Comply with legal obligations
                        
                    

                    
                        3. Sharing of Information
                        
                            We do not sell or rent your personal information. We may share your data only in these circumstances:
                        
                        Service Providers
                        
                            We share information with trusted partners who perform services such as payment processing, technical support, and analytics.
                        
                        Legal Compliance
                        
                            We may disclose your information if required by law, legal processes, or to protect the rights and safety of Atlantic Server, our users, or others.
                        
                    

                    
                        4. Data Security
                        
                            We take data security seriously and implement various measures to protect your information, including:
                        
                        
                            Encryption for data in transit and at rest
                            Regular security monitoring and vulnerability assessments
                            Strict access controls and authentication procedures
                            Staff training and security awareness programs
                        
                    

                    
                        5. Data Retention
                        
                            We retain personal information as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy, comply with legal obligations, and resolve disputes. When no longer needed, data is securely deleted or anonymized.
                        
                    

                    
                        6. Your Rights
                        
                            Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have rights to:
                        
                        
                            Access your personal data
                            Request correction of incorrect or incomplete data
                            Request deletion of your personal data
                            Object to or restrict certain data processing
                            Request data portability
                        
                        
                            To exercise these rights, please contact us using the details provided below.
                        
                    

                    
                        7. Cookies and Tracking
                        
                            We use cookies and similar technologies to improve our services and analyze usage. You can control or disable cookies via your browser settings, but this may impact your experience.
                        
                    

                    
                        8. International Transfers
                        
                            Your information may be transferred to and processed in other countries. We take steps to ensure appropriate safeguards are in place to protect your data in accordance with applicable laws.
                        
                    

                    
                        9. Children's Privacy
                        
                            Atlantic Server services are not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If we learn that we have collected such data, we will take steps to delete it promptly.
                        
                    

                    
                        10. Updates to Privacy Policy
                        
                            We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will notify you of significant changes by posting the updated policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.
                        
                    

                    
                        11. Contact Us

        Get Started
        
            
        
    


    
    
        BIHOST
        üåü Solusi Harga Murah üåü
        
            <VPS KVM NAT/>
            <LXC Container/>
            <Indonesia Server/>
        
        
            VPS NAT & Container berkualitas dengan harga yang ramah di kantong. Berlokasi di Indonesia untuk latensi terbaik dan performa maksimal untuk proyek Anda.
        
        
             Hubungi Sekarang
        
    
    
        
            // Server Specifications
const server = {
  location: "Indonesia",
  cpu: "Intel Xeon E5-2670v2 x4 & Intel Xeon E5-2420v2 x2",
  ram: 288 GB,
  storage: 3192 GB
};
        
    

    
        Semua yang Anda Butuhkan untuk Berkembang
        Platform komprehensif kami menyediakan semua alat dan fitur yang Anda butuhkan untuk menerapkan, mengelola, dan menskalakan aplikasi Anda dengan percaya diri.
    

    
        
            
                
            
            Secepat Kilat
            Terapkan aplikasi Anda dalam hitungan detik dengan infrastruktur kami yang dioptimalkan dan jaringan CDN global.
        

        
            
                
            
            Keamanan Enterprise
            Fitur keamanan canggih termasuk proteksi DDoS, sertifikat SSL, dan pencadangan rutin.
        

        
            
                
            
            Upgrade Mudah
            Tingkatkan sumber daya server Anda dengan mulus melalui panel kontrol kami, tanpa perlu konfigurasi yang rumit.
        

        
            
                
            
            Monitoring Real-time
            Pantau server dan aplikasi Anda dengan analitik terperinci dan peringatan instan.
        

        
            
                
            
            Managed Database
            Solusi database yang dikelola sepenuhnya dengan pencadangan otomatis dan ketersediaan tinggi.
        

        
            
                
            
            Dukungan 24/7
            Tim dukungan ahli tersedia sepanjang waktu untuk membantu Anda dengan masalah teknis apa pun.
        
    

    
        Harga yang Sesuai Kebutuhan Anda
        Pilih paket yang paling sesuai dengan skala proyek Anda, mulai dari proyek kecil hingga skala enterprise.

            Sempurna untuk proyek percobaan
            10K/bulan

                 1 GB RAM
                 15 GB HDD Storage
                 10 Mbps Bandwidth
            
            Contact Sales

                 2 GB RAM
                 20 GB NVME Storage
                 Unlimited Bandwidth

            Untuk produksi skala menengah ke atas
            40K/bulan
            
                 2 vCPU Cores
                 4 GB RAM
                 30 GB NVME Storage
                 Unlimited Bandwidth

While We strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect Your Personal Data, We cannot guarantee its absolute security. Our Service does not address anyone under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from anyone under the age of 13. If You are a parent or guardian and You are aware that Your child has provided Us with Personal Data, please contact Us. If We become aware that We have collected Personal Data from anyone under the age of 13 without verification of parental consent, We take steps to remove that information from Our servers. If We need to rely on consent as a legal basis for processing Your information and Your country requires consent from a parent, We may require Your parent's consent before We collect and use that information. Links to Other Websites Our Service may contain links to other websites that are not operated by Us. If You click on a third party link, You will be directed to that third party's site. We strongly advise You to review the Privacy Policy of every site You visit. We have no control over and assume no responsibility for the content, privacy policies or practices of any third party sites or services. Changes to this Privacy Policy We may update Our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify You of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. We will let You know via email and/or a prominent notice on Our Service, prior to the change becoming effective and update the "Last updated" date at the top of this Privacy Policy. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes. Changes to this Privacy Policy are effective when they are posted on this page. If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, You can contact us: By email: termai.api@gmail.com
